{"tid":1185611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有香港人都有義務悼念六四","createTime":"2019-06-04T11:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T12:07:47.000Z","uid":196445,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e22bf2caad37f1e5d63e281fe6d9aa444936aec6","tid":1185611,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"冇錯係悼念自己已經死去嘅中國人身份<br />\n<br />\n六四就係叫醒班仲發𡁵民主回歸夢嘅人<br />\n冇六四，平安過渡九七嘅話香港人唔可以提早睇清共產黨真面目<br />\n同冇彭定康政改。<br />\n<br />\n可能23條立法都冇人理<br />\n<br />\n所以應該慶幸有六四發生，等香港人早啲準備97<br />\n<br />\n最後鄧小平條矮仔冚家剷食屎狗賤種支那狗，而家喺地獄開唔開心啊屌你老母，個天有報應㗎，你有生之年都淨係見到米字旗喺香港飄揚"},{"pid":"ab9b8040439836b967a32254e366cae8e5f828d0","tid":1185611,"uid":152230,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"中國既事關香港人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d96da2363881ec5db6818aa93364bac31d27df8","tid":1185611,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"90幾歲先死真係惡有惡報呀"},{"pid":"d15adc855c07d6bca84ea84fea227dac6f0a477d","tid":1185611,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9b8040439836b967a32254e366cae8e5f828d0","tid":1185611,"uid":152230,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"中國既事關香港人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"唔好俾標題呃咗，悼念係講自己嘅愛國心"},{"pid":"330bbb265119997c10a4da2560511f66bfb378fd","tid":1185611,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"點解你們唔紀念二二八啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7f9248ebf5fcb12fd16a7e9178d274337ad650","tid":1185611,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"屌可能我表達得唔好，我唔係中華膠呀"},{"pid":"a392d492e16148c4a500ff2d8efd8a690d1ed6f5","tid":1185611,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,